      "Text": "Security update for systemd",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for systemd fixes the following issues:\n\nSecurity issues fixed:\n\n- CVE-2026-40226: nspawn: escape-to-host via malformed optional config file (bsc#1261400).\n\nOther updates and bugfixes:\n\n- Import commit 260e668bfa (bsc#1267647 bsc#1262305 bsc#1267644).\n- Import commit 58e5d2e21e (bsc#1261982).\n- Import commit 4bd91117cc (bsc#1261983).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
